1
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,519
You've lost a lot of blood.

2
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:09,159
You'll need a few days' rest to recover.

3
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:11,439
I'll get you some blood-building medicine.

4
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:14,040
That way you'll heal faster.

5
00:01:14,079 --> 00:01:16,680
And it'll be easier for you to leave.

6
00:01:16,799 --> 00:01:17,840
You know medicine too?

7
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,640
Because I'm a patient myself.

8
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:22,280
The doctor said I have a serious illness.

9
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,959
I might not have long to live.

10
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,200
Three years.

11
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,480
Two years.

12
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,280
Or maybe tomorrow.

13
00:01:29,959 --> 00:01:32,519
Doesn't that make you sad?

14
00:01:32,719 --> 00:01:33,519
Not really.

15
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,480
At least I'm still alive right now.

16
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:39,079
I have lots of big brothers and sisters,

17
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:39,959
and uncles who care about me.

18
00:01:40,159 --> 00:01:42,480
Actually, I'm grateful for my illness.

19
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:43,439
Because of it,

20
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:45,680
I can use what I've learned

21
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,280
to help more people.

22
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:49,879
Su Yang doesn't really dislike you.

23
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:51,680
It's just that at mealtimes,

24
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,000
he always has to grumble a bit.

25
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,599
If...

26
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,799
if you really have nowhere to go,

27
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:58,000
why not stay here?

28
00:01:58,239 --> 00:02:00,079
I don't know how much longer I'll live.

29
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,840
If one day I'm gone,

30
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:05,359
no one will clean up for Su Yang anymore.

31
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:08,360
Someone he doesn't hate needs to look after him.

32
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,120
Otherwise,

33
00:02:09,159 --> 00:02:11,080
he'll just get triggered again.

34
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,199
Su Yang's back!

35
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,520
This is for you.

36
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,199
In it goes.

37
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,919
Uncle Houzi, come eat!

38
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,319
Let me help you.

39
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,240
It's fine, I've got it.

40
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,400
I'll do it, I'll do it.

41
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,319
Okay, okay.

42
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,560
Su Yang promised not to kill randomly.

43
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,360
Sit down.

44
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,439
Sit.

45
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,479
Oh right,

46
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:17,000
I forgot you can't eat

47
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,400
anything greasy or salty right now.

48
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:20,639
I made you some porridge for lunch.

49
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,479
Here.

50
00:03:30,319 --> 00:03:32,120
It shouldn't be too hot.

51
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:33,000
Perfect.

52
00:03:33,759 --> 00:03:35,240
Still warm.

53
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,199
Thank you.

54
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,199
You're welcome.

55
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:49,960
I'm full.

56
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:59,479
I'm apologizing on Su Yang's behalf.

57
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,960
He may act crazy sometimes,

58
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:03,960
but everything he does

59
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:05,759
has a reason behind it.

60
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:08,120
He doesn't truly mean to harm people.

61
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,240
I don't expect you to forgive him,

62
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:14,759
but if one day in the future,

63
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,439
you see Su Yang lying in a pool of blood,

64
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,079
barely breathing,

65
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,399
please just don't deliver the final blow.

66
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,920
Su Yang has said

67
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,839
that day will come for him eventually.

68
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,160
Let's eat.

69
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,079
From this moment on,

70
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:48,079
we're establishing the Lingxiao

71
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,399
Network Surveillance Division.

72
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,079
Everyone's working overtime.

73
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:55,360
Track online forum comments 24/7.

74
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:58,279
Maintain full monitoring and screening.

75
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,199
Keep a tight watch on Black Street.

76
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,360
In three days,

77
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:02,279
I want to see on my desk

78
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,480
a complete list

79
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:06,399
containing 80 percent

80
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:08,560
of Shanhai City's Blessed Ones.

81
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,560
Can you do it?

82
00:05:12,639 --> 00:05:13,399
Alright, meeting adjourned.

83
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:18,439
The reason I came here today

84
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:20,959
is to announce something to all of you.

85
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,439
Our Shanhai City

86
00:05:23,079 --> 00:05:25,199
will form a squad of Blessed Ones.

87
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,720
The name

88
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,480
is Lingxiao.

89
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,360
In mythology,

90
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:33,800
Lingxiao represents the heavenly court above.

91
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,680
And now,

92
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,319
in the name of Lingxiao,

93
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:39,199
we fulfill our duty to protect,

94
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,600
guarding every home in Shanhai City.

95
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,879
Even if

96
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,879
it costs us our lives.

97
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:47,800
Are you confident?

98
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,680
Yes!

99
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:57,279
Limpy hates being disturbed during his nap.

100
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,319
Scared?

101
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,639
Me? Scared?

102
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,160
Tongtong's been taken.

103
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,279
What about Su Yang?

104
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:19,120
Still don't know.

105
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,600
It was that guy Houzi

106
00:06:20,879 --> 00:06:23,160
who used his last breath to warn us.

107
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,720
What the hell is he thinking this time?

108
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,720
Based on what the Marketing Department

109
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,120
has compiled so far,

110
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:36,360
the immortals seem to randomly select

111
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,079
mortals with similar personalities

112
00:06:38,079 --> 00:06:38,800
to bestow blessings upon.

113
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:41,000
The Blessed can borrow the immortals' power.

114
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:41,839
Randomly?

115
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,480
Yes, with no discernible pattern.

116
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,000
And so far,

117
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,160
the Blessed Ones

118
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,839
can only borrow very limited abilities.

119
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:52,399
Mostly strength, speed,

120
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:54,319
just basic attribute boosts.

121
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:56,879
According to algorithmic analysis,

122
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:59,439
this may be because the Blessed Ones

123
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,720
aren't strong enough yet.

124
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:02,480
As their physical strength improves,

125
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,360
they may access more techniques.

126
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:05,720
Starting now,

127
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,040
spare no expense.

128
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,560
Hire the Blessed Ones

129
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,439
to keep studying immortal blessings

130
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,839
for deeper analysis.

131
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,000
Money is no object.

132
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,279
Understood.

133
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:29,480
Youngest Blessed One emerges:

134
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,639
a ten-year-old boy,

135
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:33,160
registered on Chunfeng Rd by his parents.

136
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:35,920
Linhai Group's CEO reveals he's a Blessed One.

137
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,519
In today's dating market,

138
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:39,680
Blessed Ones are in the highest demand.

139
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,560
Stop.

140
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,759
Stop, stop.

141
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:42,800
The point is,

142
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,720
among all these Blessed Ones,

143
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:47,959
is there anyone exceptionally powerful?

144
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:48,680
Yes.

145
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:49,519
Who?

146
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:50,959
Xu Siguo.

147
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,879
Who's Xu Siguo?

148
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:54,879
Don't know.

149
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,680
I don't have any info on him.

150
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,720
Then go find some!

151
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:01,720
Go, hurry up!

152
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:04,600
Fast, fast, fast!

153
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,720
I really do like that girl.

154
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,480
Just follow your own heart.

155
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,800
Something big happened!

156
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,600
Hurry, go deliver the news!

157
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:22,040
Got it!

158
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:22,680
Sangou.

159
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,720
Five minutes.

160
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,399
Excuse me.

161
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:37,480
Can I help you?

162
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:39,279
You know what I want to ask, right?

163
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,679
No, I...

164
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:42,919
I'm in a bad mood right now.

165
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:45,120
I'd appreciate your cooperation.

166
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,200
I really don't know what you mean.

167
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,000
I told you,

168
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,559
I'm in a bad mood.

169
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:54,720
And I'm in a hurry.

170
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:55,639
Tongtong.

171
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:57,159
Tongtong left Black Street this morning.

172
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,639
She was kidnapped on her way back.

173
00:08:58,759 --> 00:09:00,279
By the time we got there, they were gone.

174
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,399
After checking surveillance footage,

175
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,440
we found they're all unregistered citizens.

176
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,320
Right now,

177
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,120
the only lead we have

178
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:08,720
is that they headed west.

179
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,639
The rest...

180
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:11,759
The rest is still under investigation.

181
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,639
Thank you.

182
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,559
They went west.

183
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,879
That's all we know.

184
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,840
West.

185
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,360
Yes.

186
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,360
That lead is way too vague.

187
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:23,600
Tongtong.

188
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,360
Tongtong.

189
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:27,480
Tongtong.

190
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:28,960
Where's Tongtong? Shut up.

191
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:30,159
Where is Tongtong?

192
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,240
From now on,

193
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,799
if you want to save Tongtong, shut your mouth.

194
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,039
Okay.

195
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:37,200
Knowing the Liu family's style,

196
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:39,360
they won't take this matter seriously.

197
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,279
Let's kill our way west.

198
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:42,679
One person every mile.

199
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:45,080
Until they give us answers.

200
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,639
Let me handle this.

201
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:52,840
Qian.

202
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:54,600
Kun.

203
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:55,919
Zhen.

204
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:57,320
Xun.

205
00:09:58,159 --> 00:09:58,759
Kan.

206
00:09:59,240 --> 00:09:59,799
Li.

207
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:01,279
Gen.

208
00:10:02,159 --> 00:10:02,799
Dui.

209
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:07,480
Fuxi's Eight Trigrams.

210
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:35,440
Ill omen. Southwest.

211
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,360
I knew you were blessed, old man.

212
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:42,120
If Tongtong hadn't been taken,

213
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:43,759
how much longer would you have hidden it?

214
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,200
I'm borrowing your car.

215
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,000
Pick it up at this time tomorrow.

216
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,440
Someone who can drive, get up here.

217
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,480
If you want to save Tongtong, sit in the back.

218
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,399
Okay.

219
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,200
Bunch of old geezers.

220
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,000
Those guys

221
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,320
have left Black Street.

222
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,759
It's time to meet the people of Black Street.

223
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,679
In case they really cause trouble,

224
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:39,799
I needed data on Shanhai's Blessed Ones.

225
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:41,159
Have you finished it?

226
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,159
Who's the strongest?

227
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,440
Su Yang.

228
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:47,919
Su Yang.

229
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:50,879
Besides him?

230
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,480
Xu Siguo.

231
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:54,759
I've heard you mention him.

232
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:55,919
Call him over.

233
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,600
He'll come with me on the operation.

234
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,080
Good chance to see his strength.

235
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:02,240
Who has contacts for other Black Street people?

236
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,399
Have someone stake out the clinic.

237
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,519
If that madman shows up,

238
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,399
make him get his ass over here ASAP.

239
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:12,720
If Tongtong dies,

240
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,320
he goes down with her.

241
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,240
Buried with her.

242
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,879
But we can't beat him.

243
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,600
Shut up.

244
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:20,399
Okay.

245
00:12:36,679 --> 00:12:37,960
There's a car tailing us.

246
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,240
Take it easy.

247
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,159
Liu family men.

248
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:10,679
Introduce yourselves.

249
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:11,879
Shanhai City.

250
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:12,879
Liu family.

251
00:13:13,159 --> 00:13:14,080
Liu Chengfeng.

252
00:14:04,279 --> 00:14:05,480
Once the seed sprouts,

253
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:08,519
the cleaner's condition will be contained.

254
00:14:32,639 --> 00:14:34,200
Madman, Limpy has news.

255
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,320
I need a favor.

256
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,799
Help my friend

257
00:14:42,559 --> 00:14:43,200
take a bath.

258
00:14:43,559 --> 00:14:44,159
Okay.

259
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,159
Thank you.

260
00:15:06,799 --> 00:15:07,480
Houzi

261
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:09,559
Thank you.

262
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:21,919
The sky...

263
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,720
seems to have gotten darker.

264
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:32,840
I know

265
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,399
you are all furious.

266
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:37,639
But this is the Liu family's negligence.

267
00:15:37,879 --> 00:15:39,679
I hope you will give us a chance

268
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,320
to handle this matter ourselves.

269
00:15:41,759 --> 00:15:42,559
I promise

270
00:15:42,879 --> 00:15:45,799
to return her safely to Black Street.

271
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,639
What do you say?

272
00:15:46,759 --> 00:15:48,919
Black Street handles its own affairs.

273
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,840
No need to trouble the Liu family.

274
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:55,120
So there's no room for negotiation?

275
00:15:55,879 --> 00:15:56,879
Well, in that case,

276
00:15:57,279 --> 00:15:58,559
I still hope all of you

277
00:15:58,559 --> 00:16:00,279
won't make this too ugly.

278
00:16:00,399 --> 00:16:01,559
After all, the Liu family

279
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,960
still has its dignity to uphold.

280
00:16:07,039 --> 00:16:08,879
When immortals comply, praises are sung.

281
00:16:09,399 --> 00:16:11,080
When they defy, what can they do to me?

282
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:12,000
Yang Jian,

283
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:12,799
manifest!

284
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:38,159
What's he doing?

285
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,759
He's going to fight.

286
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:42,759
Why fight?

287
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:44,000
Because you said

288
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,720
the Liu family needs its dignity too.

289
00:16:52,679 --> 00:16:53,440
Nice.

290
00:16:54,279 --> 00:16:55,279
He's going to fight you.

291
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:56,799
Fight me?

292
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,119
So weak.

293
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,599
I'd like to ask,

294
00:17:09,319 --> 00:17:11,240
is he really, as of now,

295
00:17:11,519 --> 00:17:16,160
the strongest Blessed One in Shanhai?

296
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:19,440
He was very eager when he signed up.

297
00:17:19,799 --> 00:17:21,319
Just a bit shy.

298
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:23,480
Then how can someone like him

299
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:25,640
be captain of Lingxiao?

300
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,119
I still can't let this go.

301
00:17:28,519 --> 00:17:30,359
I want to confirm one last time.

302
00:17:30,839 --> 00:17:32,519
Is there anyone stronger than him?

303
00:17:37,079 --> 00:17:38,000
Okay, okay, okay.

304
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:40,400
Come back.

305
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:41,880
Come back, come back, come back.

306
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,519
Come on, come on.

307
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:46,119
I... I can still do it.

308
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,240
I know, I know, I know.

309
00:17:48,759 --> 00:17:50,279
But haven't you noticed

310
00:17:50,759 --> 00:17:52,240
the guy over there is stronger than us?

311
00:17:56,119 --> 00:17:56,839
Um,

312
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,160
sorry about this.

313
00:17:58,599 --> 00:18:00,000
Sorry to waste everyone's time.

314
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:02,519
Go do whatever you were doing.

315
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:04,319
Don't mind us at all.

316
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:06,079
We're all a bit messed up in the head.

317
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:12,680
I'll do it.

318
00:18:16,799 --> 00:18:17,440
Idiot.

319
00:18:18,599 --> 00:18:20,720
You have to pull it open.

320
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,039
Tongtong!

321
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:30,960
Tongtong!

322
00:18:34,039 --> 00:18:36,000
This Limpy moves pretty fast.

323
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,319
Let's go check it out.

324
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:41,640
Let's go.

325
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:51,200
What are you doing?

326
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,559
I'm commandeering your carriage.

327
00:18:58,720 --> 00:18:59,519
Tongtong!

328
00:19:00,039 --> 00:19:00,920
Tongtong!

329
00:19:02,039 --> 00:19:02,680
Tongtong!

330
00:19:06,079 --> 00:19:07,440
You killed Tongtong!

331
00:19:09,519 --> 00:19:11,440
I'll fight you to the death!
